        <p>&gt; <span data-i18n="miscellaneous-cybersecurity"></span></p>
        <p>&gt; <span data-i18n="miscellaneous-machinelearning"></span></p>
        <p>&gt; <span data-i18n="miscellaneous-barcelonaqbit"></span> <a href="http://www.barcelonaqbit.com" target="_blank">Barcelonaqbit</a>.</p>
